OL,3,CInquiry due to begin into death of
OL,4,Cserial killer Peter Tobin
OL,6,FAn inquiry is due to begin into the
OL,7,Fdeath of serial killer Peter Tobin.
OL,9,FHe was serving a prison term for
OL,10,Fraping and murdering Polish student
OL,11,FAngelika Kluk, 23, and hiding her body
OL,12,Funder the floor of a Glasgow church in
OL,13,F2006.
OL,15,FHe also murdered student Dinah
OL,16,FMcNicol, and 15-year-old schoolgirl
OL,17,FVicky Hamilton.
