OL,3,CInquiry due to begin into death of
OL,4,Cserial killer Peter Tobin
OL,6,FTheir bodies were discovered buried in
OL,7,Fthe back garden of Tobin's former home
OL,8,Fin Margate, 17 years after they
OL,9,Fdisappeared.
OL,11,FTobin had been receiving palliative
OL,12,Fcare but sustained a fall in his
OL,13,Fprison cell the day before his death.
OL,15,FHe was taken from HMP Edinburgh to the
OL,16,FEdinburgh Royal Infirmary on 9
OL,17,FSeptember 2022, and subsequently died
OL,18,Fon 8 October 2022.
