OL,3,CInquiry due to begin into death of
OL,4,Cserial killer Peter Tobin
OL,6,FThe Crown Office and Procurator Fiscal
OL,7,FService (COPFS) has lodged a First
OL,8,FNotice to begin the court process for
OL,9,Fa Fatal Accident Inquiry into the
OL,10,Fdeath of the 76-year-old.
OL,12,FA Preliminary Hearing will be held on
OL,13,F27 May 2024 at Edinburgh Sheriff Court.
