OL,3,CInquiry due to begin into death of
OL,4,Cserial killer Peter Tobin
OL,6,FThe purpose of a Fatal Accident
OL,7,FInquiry (FAI) is to determine the
OL,8,Fcause of death, the circumstances in
OL,9,Fwhich the deaths occurred, and to
OL,10,Festablish what, if any, reasonable
OL,11,Fprecautions could have been taken, and
OL,12,Fcould be implemented in the future, to
OL,13,Fminimise the risk of future deaths in
OL,14,Fsimilar circumstances.
