OL,3,CInquiry due to begin into death of
OL,4,Cserial killer Peter Tobin
OL,6,FProcurator Fiscal Andy Shanks, who
OL,7,Fleads on fatalities investigations for
OL,8,FCOPFS, said: "The Lord Advocate
OL,9,Fconsiders that the death of Peter
OL,10,FTobin occurred while in legal custody
OL,11,Fand as such a Fatal Accident Inquiry
OL,12,Fis mandatory.
OL,14,F"The lodging of the First Notice
OL,15,Fenables FAI proceedings to commence
OL,16,Funder the direction of the Sheriff."
